column1: 1. Delinquency figures are cases petitioned for fiscal year 2012.
2. Status figures are cases petitioned for fiscal year 2012.
3. Dependency figures are abuse and/or neglect petitions and Department of Family Services termination of parental rights petitions for fiscal year 2012.
